Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I lost 31 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then I found something worse — the 90 percent win rate I'd been citing in public all week was basically fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.46,0:00:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}9 years in crypto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}AI trades my thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The bot hit a stop loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Single trade loss of 31 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}First real loss of the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I sat down to review.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}On a whim I stretched the backtest window from 5 days to 13 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Same strategy — 13 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Minus 46 percent return.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Minus 56 percent max drawdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Translation — the 90 percent win rate I'd been proud of for a week was a number hiding in the narrowest possible window.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Not dishonest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Just incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And incomplete when money's involved means — wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:01:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You know what your proudest number usually looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's usually hiding in the corner you don't want to stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Stretching the window is the scariest thing you can do to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Your number might survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It might not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.06,0:01:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You don't know till you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It didn't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 7 tomorrow — I decided to tear the whole thing apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow along.
